data.description: Prime 5 acres development opportunity offering a blank canvas for your vision.  Nestled in a desirable location, this expansive parcel boasts limitless potential for residential projects.  Explore the possibilities of crafting a vibrant community or an innovative business hub.  Don't miss the chance to shape the future on these versatile acres. The property is located 1 mile from Target/Home Depot, 2 miles from DCH Regional Medical and 2.5 miles from The University of Alabama.
